{
  "arquivo": "ca03_mv5_01",
  "total": 34,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "%p-2;――%p; Ah.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "What's up?\\nFound a good souvenir?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Not a souvenir,\\nbut Uesugi-san is running over here.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "M-Miku!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Huh, Futaro?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I-I-I'm gonna check out another store.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Wait up, Miku!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Uesugi-san, please, stop!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Futaro-kun, calm down a bit!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Oh, Yotsuba and Ichika?\\nYou guys were here, huh.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I-I see.\\nYou were so desperate that you didn't even notice us.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Sorry...\\nI just wanted to talk to Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Well, don't you think you're a bit too eager?\\nIf you charge at someone like that,\\nanyone would run away.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It can't be helped!\\nIf Miku's running away, then\\nI have to chase her!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Being serious is a good thing, but\\nyou might be making Miku nervous right now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "You were so fired up, now,\\nit surprised me, too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Is that so?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "From Miku's point of view,\\nit might seem like\\nyou're closing in...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What do you mean by 'closing in'?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "In that case%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Yotsuba, stop!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Futaro-kun doesn't know that we heard everything\\nfrom Itsuki-chan.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "...Ah!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, what's wrong?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "N-no!\\nIt's nothing.\\nBy closing in, I mean...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "When you came charging over earlier,\\nyour face looked super scary!\\nLike a raging bull!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Really? Was I making that face again?!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Damn. It's the same as yesterday.\\n I'm just thinking about myself\\n and putting Miku's feelings second again...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "You have to be gentler.\\nGirls are delicate, like soap bubbles.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...That's true.\\nCome to think of it, I had a hard time\\ngetting through your guys' defenses.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "But, you were able to do it, weren't you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, thanks.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "We're cheering for you!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}